@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Data Collection</h3>
        <p>Contract Monthly Claims System (CMCS) collects personal data such as names, contact details, employee IDs, work hours, and financial information to process monthly claims. We collect this data directly from employees or authorized representatives.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Use of Data</h3>
        <p>Your data is used for claims processing, payment calculation, and verification. Data may be shared with payroll providers and regulatory authorities as required by law.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Data Protection & Security</h3>
        <p>Your data is encrypted and access is restricted to authorized personnel only. We implement role-based access controls to ensure data visibility is limited based on user roles.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Data Retention</h3>
        <p>Claims data is retained for up to <strong>[X years]</strong> for business and legal purposes. Upon request, personal data may be deleted unless retention is required by law.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Employee Rights</h3>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Access:</strong> You can request access to your personal data at any time.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Correction:</strong> Request updates to any incorrect or outdated data.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Portability:</strong> You may export your data in a machine-readable format.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Cookies & Tracking</h3>
        <p>We use cookies to enhance system performance and security. You can control cookie preferences directly in your browser settings.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Data Sharing</h3>
        <p>CMCS does not sell your data. Data may be shared with government agencies or third-party providers where required.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
        <p>This policy may be updated periodically. Significant changes will be communicated promptly.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any concerns or questions, please contact our Data Privacy Officer at <a href="mailto:privacy@cmcs.com">privacy@cmcs.com</a> or <a href="tel:+1234567890">+123 456 7890</a>.</p>
    </section>
</div>
